arget="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>阅读有关俱乐部的更多信息并购买球衣。</p><p>这支苏格兰乐队于 2022 年首次与 Lajee Celtic 合作， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primal-scream-collaborate-with-aida-celtic-for-football-shirt-that-raises-funds-for-palestinian-refugee-team-3329322">首次推出“Palestinadelica”品牌</a>。前曼联球星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eric-cantona">埃里克·坎通纳 (Eric Cantona)</a>也加入了他们的促销活动，并在 Instagram 上穿着这件球衣摆姿势。</p><p>无数其他音乐界人士也对以色列-加沙冲突直言不讳。</p><p> 5月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramore-call-for-gaza-aid-donations-we-do-not-believe-that-support-for-our-palestinian-friends-and-family-is-anti-semitism-3760635">帕拉莫尔呼吁通过“拯救儿童”组织捐款支持加沙</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-brian-eno-fontaines-dc-carlos-oconnell-michael-stipe-bastille-dan-smith-read-voices-for-gaza-letters-3756154">方丹特区、REM和巴士底狱的成员布赖恩·伊诺则宣读了加沙受苦受难的巴勒斯坦人的来信，</a>作为“为加沙之声”倡议的一部分。</p><p> Paul Weller<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-shares-support-for-all-eyes-on-rafah-3760399">和 Dua Lipa</a>也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-weller-shares-support-for-palestine-am-i-against-genocides-and-ethnic-cleansing-yes-i-am-funnily-enough-3760050">表达了对巴勒斯坦的支持</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fka-twigs-london-fundraiser-gaza-sudan-aid-mustafa-clairo-3772252">FKA Twigs 则出现在伦敦的筹款演出中支持加沙和苏丹</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/damon-albarn-speaks-on-palestine-at-glastonbury-importance-of-voting-in-uk-general-election-next-week-3769928">达蒙·阿尔本 (Damon Albarn) 今年在格拉斯顿伯里 (Glastonbury) 的舞台上谈到了这场冲突</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/record-labels-promoters-and-more-come-together-to-call-for-cultural-boycott-of-israel-3763930">一群唱片公司和推广者则呼吁通过巴勒斯坦以色列学术和文化抵制运动 (PACBI) 对以色列进行文化抵制</a>。</p><p>这场冲突也对今年的音乐节产生了重大影响， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/over-100-acts-have-now-dropped-out-of-the-great-escape-2024-in-gaza-boycott-with-support-from-massive-attack-3756090">超过 100 名表演者退出了 The Great Escape，</a>以声援巴勒斯坦并抗议巴克莱银行对音乐节的赞助。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/more-acts-drop-out-of-latitude-2024-of-barclays-sponsorship-we-can-make-a-difference-festivals-can-make-meaningful-change-3762429">出于同样的原因，有几个名字退出了 Latitude——</a>尽管<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/enter-shikari-speak-out-as-barclays-pull-out-of-download-latitude-and-isle-of-wight-festivals-after-boycott-3765821">巴克莱后来退出了该活动</a>。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/eurovision-boycotts-protest-fans-watching-2024-israel-palestine-3755156">今年的欧洲歌唱大赛也因以色列参加比赛而引发争议和抗议</a>。</p><p>与此同时，Primal Scream <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primal-scream-announce-first-album-in-eight-years-come-ahead-listen-to-cosmic-new-single-love-insurrection-3775839">上个月宣布了他们的新专辑《Come Ahead》</a> ，这是他们八年来的第一张专辑。该专辑将于11月8日发行，主打单曲是《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primal-scream-announce-first-album-in-eight-years-come-ahead-listen-to-cosmic-new-single-love-insurrection-3775839">Love Resurrection</a> 》。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primal-scream-team-up-on-palestinadelica-shirt-for-refugee-football-team-3782235">难民足球队的“Palestinadelica”球衣上的原始尖叫队 (Primal Scream)</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
