set="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Springsteen-and-Bryan.-Credit-Gus-Stewart-and-Keith-Griner-min.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Springsteen-and-Bryan.-Credit-Gus-Stewart-and-Keith-Griner-min-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Springsteen-and-Bryan.-Credit-Gus-Stewart-and-Keith-Griner-min-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Springsteen-and-Bryan.-Credit-Gus-Stewart-and-Keith-Griner-min-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Springsteen-and-Bryan.-Credit-Gus-Stewart-and-Keith-Griner-min-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Springsteen-and-Bryan.-Credit-Gus-Stewart-and-Keith-Griner-min-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀</a>本周在费城演出《大西洋城》时与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zach-bryan">扎克·布莱恩</a>一起作为惊喜嘉宾登上舞台。</p><p>周三（8 月 7 日），在布莱恩“Quittin Time Tour”的第二场费城演出中，两人表演了标志性的斯普林斯汀曲目以及他们的新合作歌曲“Sandpaper”。</p><p> 《Atlantic City》取自 Springsteen 1982 年的专辑《Nebraska》，是一首精简的原声歌曲，歌词令人难以忘怀，声音令人脊背发凉。</p><p>两人一起唱了标志性的副歌：“<em>一切都会死去，宝贝，这是事实/但也许有一天死去的一切都会回来/化妆，把头发打扮得漂亮/今晚在大西洋城见我</em>。”</p><p>然后他们进入了布莱恩最新专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/us-country-star-zach-bryan-releases-new-album-featuring-bruce-springsteen-and-john-mayer-3771934">伟大的美国酒吧场景</a>》中斯普林斯汀主打的歌曲《Sandpaper》。新项目还邀请了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-mayer">约翰·梅尔</a>和约翰·莫兰。</p><p>费城的音乐会观众在<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@medstudentmags/video/7400591141994843423?embed_source=121374463%2C121451205%2C121439635%2C121433650%2C121404358%2C121351166%2C121331973%2C120811592%2C120810756%3Bnull%3Bembed_blank&amp;refer=embed&amp;referer_url=www.rollingstone.com%2Fmusic%2Fmusic-news%2Fzach-bryan-bruce-springsteen-duet-atlantic-city-1235076133%2F&amp;referer_video_id=7400591141994843423" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok</a>上发布了舞台上共享时刻的片段。请观看以下内容： </p><blockquote c